/system-research/agents/researcher/instruct.md:L6-L16`). Ships **no functions of its own** — its tasks reach the web through `system-global`'s `webSearch`/`webFetch`, allow-listed per task. |\n | **`system-appbuilder`** | `app-architect` | `build_app` *(default)* | Builds a whole application — **the store-catalog template path**. Runs the `build_app` tasklist and reports; may delegate one slice to a specialist (`sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/app-architect/instruct.md:L29-L54`). |\n-| | `automator` | *(none — model-driven)* | Builds/extends the app **in the LIVE project**: `writeProjectTable` (with a third `rows` arg that seeds data at creation), `writeProjectHook`, `writeProjectEvent`, `writeProjectApi`, `writeProjectPage` (`sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/instruct.md:L16-L33`). This is THING's default app path. |\n+| | `automator` | *(none — model-driven)* | Builds/extends the app **in the LIVE project**: `writeProjectTable` (with a third `rows` arg that seeds data at creation), `writeProjectHook`, `writeProjectEvent`, `writeProjectApi`, `writeProjectPage`, and `writeProjectComponent` for reusable in-app UI (`sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/instruct.md:L16-L40`). This is THING's default app path. For a tailored choice, it can add a view/form component and must treat a dismissed form as no change (`sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/instruct.md:L65-L67`). |\n | | `data-modeler` | *(none)* | One slice: JSON table schemas via `writeTableSchema(name, schema)`; every table/column/relation carries a real `description` (`sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/data-modeler/charter.md:L1-L6`). |\n | | `api-author` | *(none)* | One slice: typed handlers via `writeApi('<route>/<METHOD>', src)`, exporting `name`/`description`/`Input`/`Output` + a default `async (input, ctx)` using `ctx.db` (`sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/api-author/instruct.md:L13-L30`). |\n | | `page-builder` | *(none)* | One slice: React pages via `writePage(route, src)`, design tokens only, data through `@app/runtime` (`sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/page-builder/charter.md:L1-L8`). |","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"07505bfe-a0f1-4aee-a3f1-2914d0a4ae88","uuid":"c6596e73-9aa0-40f5-b070-3fcc5f612b03","timestamp":"2026-07-14T17:17:44.440Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"504:// ═══ ACT XIV — served vault and browser-facing contract ═════════════════════════\n534:// ═══ whole-session invariants and artifacts ═════════════════════════════════════\ndiff --git a/libs/core/src/spaces/prompt-contract.test.ts b/libs/core/src/spaces/prompt-contract.test.ts\nindex 2e23801..ac68b71 100644\n--- a/libs/core/src/spaces/prompt-contract.test.ts\n+++ b/libs/core/src/spaces/prompt-contract.test.ts\n@@ -69,6 +69,16 @@ describe('system-appbuilder/automator — attribution survives the seed', () =>\n   });\n });\n \n+describe('system-appbuilder/automator — custom choice components', () => {\n+  it('tells the builder to handle a dismissed tailored form as no change', () => {\n+    const instruct = readFileSync(join(SYSTEM_SPACES, 'system-appbuilder', 'agents', 'automator', 'instruct.md'), 'utf8');\n+    expect(instruct).toMatch(/components\\/view\\/<Name>\\.tsx/);\n+    expect(instruct).toMatch(/matching form component/i);\n+    expect(instruct).toMatch(/dismissed.*null|null.*no change/i);\n+    expect(instruct).toMatch(/no change/i);\n+  });\n+});\n+\n describe('user-thing/thing — the ingest turn must ASK, and must not leak its plumbing', () => {\n   const instruct = () => readFileSync(join(SYSTEM_SPACES, 'user-thing', 'agents', 'thing', 'instruct.md'), 'utf8');\n \ndiff --git a/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/instruct.md b/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/instruct.md\nindex 1371012..ef6f662 100644\n--- a/libs/core/sys